data.description: Welcome to paradise! This exquisite 4 bed, 3 bath, 2500 sqft home sits on 8 acres of sheer serenity. Step inside the nice-sized great room, complete with a cozy bench sitting area, perfect for relaxation and connection. Unwind in the game room, where endless fun awaits. The updated kitchen is a culinary enthusiast's dream, featuring stainless appliances, a stylish backsplash, durable countertops, and custom cabinets for seamless organization. New vinyl floors add a touch of modern elegance throughout. Experience convenience and privacy with the split wing floor plan. The huge storage room offers versatility, ready to be transformed into an office, exercise haven, or creative space. Retreat to the master suite, boasting a large soaking tub and separate shower stall, creating your own personal oasis. Outside, the backyard beckons with a spacious covered patio and abundant space for your beloved animals. Don't miss this chance to own your dream home, where tranquility meets luxury.
